%p
  Welcome to
  =link_to "Dabble Me", "https://#{ENV['MAIN_DOMAIN']}"
  \- the simple & private journal that you'll actually use! Since you're new here, we're going to make it easy for you to write your first entry.
%p
  %b How's your day going?
  Just reply to this email with your answer, and it's instantly saved in your Dabble Me account.
%p
  Helpful tips:
  %ol
    %li
      It's okay to keep it simple! Even one sentence about how your day is going is just fine.
      %br
      %br
    %li
      Only you can read what you write. That means there's no wrong way to do this.
      %br
      %br
    %li
      Tag your entries with #hashtags to make it easy to find related posts.
      %br
      %br
    - if @user.is_free?
      %li
        As a free user, you'll receive an email every other week on Sunday.
        %br
        %br
      %li
        Unlock premium features like changing email frequency, editing entries, and attaching photos to your reply by subscribing to
        =link_to("Dabble Me PRO", "https://#{ENV['MAIN_DOMAIN']}/subscribe")+"."
%hr{:style=>"margin-top: 20px;margin-bottom: 20px;border: 0;border-top: 2px solid whiteSmoke;"}
%p
  You can always email #{@user.user_key}@#{ENV['SMTP_DOMAIN']} to post new entries&nbsp;
  %i> (hint: add this to your contacts)
  \.
%P
  For reference, your username is: #{@user.email}
%p
  %i
    P.S. If you received this email by error, you can
    =link_to "unsubscribe", "https://#{ENV['MAIN_DOMAIN']}/settings/#{@user.user_key}"
    to stop all future emails.
